UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.Label.Descripti: A localized name to describe what these classes are in the UI. Appears as the name of the tab in the Map Key Menu as well as in the UI itself. Choose "Custom Label" to enter your own non-localized label.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.PopupAutoSelect: A time in seconds for when a class is automatically selected and the Popup UI closes. Setting this to zero seconds hides the timer.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.Enabled.Descrip: A way to turn all of the functionality on or off including whether the Popup UI appears and if the UI appears in the Map key menu.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.EnableWhenRecei: Allow the UI to appear when triggered as a Popup UI or in the Map key menu.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ChangeOnNextRes: Delays the Class change until the next respawn rather than changing the class immediately when selected.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.DisableWhenRece: Makes it so the UI won't appear as a Popup UI or in the Player Menu, even if Activated.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ShowInMapKeyMen: Should the UI appear as a new tab in the Map key menu?
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.AlwaysGrantItem: Should the class selector UI always grant items on respawn?
UserOptionDefinition.B1A3478046C0D048721D22ABF309154B: Show HUD Message Post Popup UI
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.PlayerCanDisabl: Shows a button in the UI allowing the player to disable seeing the Popup UI on respawn. If the UI is visible in the Map key menu, the player will still be able to change their Class there.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ShowPopupUIWhen: Shows the Popup UI if the device is enabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.CustomPluralLab: The plural form of a custom label that appears in the UI (ex: "Classes" not "Class"). Limited to a maximum of 24 characters. The pre-defined list of labels gets localized into other languages. This value will be non-localized.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.CustomSingularL: The singular form of a custom label that appears in the UI (ex: "Class" not "Classes"). Limited to a maximum of 24 characters. The pre-defined list of labels gets localized into other languages. This value will be non-localized.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.WhenClassSelect: Triggered when a player selects a Class.
Triggered when a player's class is changed via the Class Selector UI.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.WhenPopupUIClos: Triggered when the Popup UI closes, either because a class was selected or because the player used the Close Button. Will not trigger when the Map Key Menu version of the UI closes.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.WhenPopupUIOpen: Triggered when the Popup UI opens.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ShowPopupUI.Des: When to automatically show the Popup UI.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ShowHUDMessageP: When to show the HUD message about which class was selected after the popup version of the UI closes. This is useful for timing events at the start of the match in case the hud message is overlapping with other player messaging at the beginning of the match.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ClassSelectorUI_C.ShowCloseButton: Whether or not the player sees the "Close" button in the UI. Without it, the player will be forced to choose a Class to exit the UI.
